<eesti>Seaduse rakendamine </eesti>
<inglise>Implementation of Act </inglise>
<eesti>(1) K&auml;esolev seadus j&otilde;ustub 2001. aasta 1. jaanuaril. </eesti>
<inglise>(1) This Act enters into force on 1 January 2001. </inglise>
<eesti>(2) Masinaid ja ohutusseadiseid v&otilde;ib 2002. aasta 1. juulini turule lasta v&otilde;i kasutusele v&otilde;tta enne k&auml;esoleva seaduse j&otilde;ustumist kehtinud &otilde;igusaktide n&otilde;udeid j&auml;rgides. </eesti>
<inglise>(2) Machinery and safety components may be placed on the market or put into service until 1 July 2002 in adherence with the requirements of legislation in force before the entry into force of this Act. </inglise>
